  new calming, sleep-themed color palette, redesigning the main form layout with
  subtle background elements and an improved progress indicator, and enhancing
  core UI components like checkboxes, radio buttons, and sliders. A significant
  part of the effort was dedicated to applying consistent styling across all
  questionnaire sections, transforming generic gray boxes into cohesive, themed
  card-style groupings. The  was revamped with a hero element and
  feature cards, and the  was updated to ensure all card headers
  and text colors aligned with the new theme, addressing initial
  inconsistencies. Additionally, a console error related to  input values
  was diagnosed and fixed by modifying the  component to safely handle
  such values. The final outcome is an app with a polished, cohesive, and
  professional aesthetic that is appropriate for a sleep health application.
